name: Js-cdn
tagline: repository to store useful js files and libraries
body:
### Overview
This project contains js files that i used to develop my differents projects. Feel free to get theses files as cdn link in your dev project.
Please don't use it as a real cdn production. Permanent availability can not be garantuee.

### Usage

The URL of js files is `http://gauthiermontavon.github.io/js-cdn/js/[js_file.js]` 

Here is the list of available js files :
* jquery.trace.js 
* var_dump.js

### jquery.trace.js 

More infos here [Ben Nadel Blog - Jquery Plugin Tracing your Selector](http://www.bennadel.com/blog/1710-jQuery-Plugin-Tracing-Your-Selector-Paths.htm)

### var_dump.js 

More infos here [Justin Phillips Blog](http://www.justinphillips.co/javascript/javascript-equivalent-to-phps-var_dump)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
